def read_image(fpath, chunk_scale=2):
    cycle = int(fpath.name.split("_")[4][:-1])
    da = xr.open_rasterio(
        fpath, chunks={"x": chunk_scale * 2048, "y": chunk_scale * 1024}
    )
    da = da.assign_coords(band=[cycle])
    return da.rename({"band": "time"})
